rows.label: tlk4342014201_msg0001
rows.name:
I always thought that Bamibami
was a no good type!

rows.label: tlk4342014201_msg0002
rows.name:
Nopon prefer eating and playing
to working any day of the week.

rows.label: tlk4342014201_msg0003
rows.name:
It was a bit suspicious for him to be
putting so much effort into working for
the group.

rows.label: tlk4342014201_msg0004
rows.name:
On the other hand, selling people out
just for a few G is such a Nopon thing
to do.
